This is a program developed to help manage tournaments, focusing on volleyball.
Created by: Brian Malsan

All information will be stored in excel spreadsheets for easy visibility

Steps:
1. Create new tournament
    a. eventually can open existing tournament
2. Get tournament information
    a. name, place, start time, format, accepted divisions
    b. # of teams, # of players/team, # of nets
3. Gather the teams and players
4. Test if all teams are cleared to play
    i.e waivers signed and team fee is paid
5. Create pools
    a. Can be either seeded of random
6. Keep track of teams wins, losses and point differential
    a. keep track of head to head
7. Determine playoffs
8. Set up bracket
9. Finish tournament
